These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, security-guard, entrepreneur
1. the security-guard is on the far left##1
2. the police-officer is on the right of the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | security-guard | entrepreneur | police-officer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, project-manager, architect
1. the architect is on the far right##1
2. the software-developer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | software-developer | project-manager | architect |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, sudoku, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | photography | sudoku | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, canadian, australian
1. the canadian is on the far right##1
2. the canadian is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | russian | australian | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, cola, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Beverage   | cola | juice | hot-chocolate |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, quad-bike, trike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | trike | quad-bike | taxi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, zombie, time-travel
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | family | zombie |

